{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"shape-rendering","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/shape-rendering","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>指定 SVG 元素<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a>的渲染模式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用参考","title":"使用参考","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类型</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><strong>auto</strong> | optimizeSpeed | crispEdges | geometricPrecision | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可运动</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">标准文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#ShapeRenderingProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"auto\">auto</dt>\n <dd>让浏览器自动权衡渲染速度、平滑度、精确度。默认是倾向于精确度而非平滑度和速度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"optimizespeed\">optimizeSpeed</dt>\n <dd>偏向渲染速度，浏览器会关闭反锯齿模式。（速度）</dd>\n <dt id=\"crispedges\">crispEdges</dt>\n <dd>偏向更加清晰锐利的边缘的渲染。浏览器在渲染的时候会关闭反锯齿模式，且会让线条的位置和宽度和显示器边缘对齐。（锐度）</dd>\n <dt id=\"geometricprecision\">geometricPrecision</dt>\n <dd>偏向渲染平滑的曲线。（平滑）</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">shape-rendering</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>optimizeSpeed<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 这个示例在 Firefox 下看区别更明显 --&gt;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>\n    <p>shape-rendering: geometricPrecision:</p>\n\n    <p><img alt=\"shape-rendering:geometricPrecision\" src=\"http://download.g63.ru/svg/shape-rendering-geometricPrecision.svg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n   </td>\n   <td>\n    <p>shape-rendering: optimizeSpeed</p>\n\n    <p><img alt=\"shape-rendering:optimizeSpeed\" src=\"http://download.g63.ru/svg/shape-rendering-optimizeSpeed.svg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>同样，你也可以在 CSS 样式中使用 shape-rendering:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>shape-rendering:optimizeSpeed;<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关联元素","title":"关联元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的元素可以使用这个属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#shape\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Shape\">Shape elements</a> »</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用参考","id":"使用参考"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"关联元素","id":"关联元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"shape-rendering","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"shape-rendering","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/shape-rendering","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/shape-rendering/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/shape-rendering","title":"shape-rendering"}],"pageTitle":"shape-rendering - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}